  - speakerName: Cow
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ba53fa4dc20dd964ea8922989dda3edf, type: 3}
    text: Excuse me?
  - speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7d3fa7d54b6bed141be46d6109a05be0, type: 3}
    text: I said mooo. I thought that was your language.
  - speakerName: Cow
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 63b391757dc92c84f9567fb28c925bd6, type: 3}
    text: Wow. That is so racist.
  - speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 7d3fa7d54b6bed141be46d6109a05be0, type: 3}
    text: Wait, what? I was just trying to be friendly.
  - speakerName: Cow
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Not because I am a cow means you can just walk up to me and say \u201Cmooo.\u201D"
